	dprr:hasNoteText "Sent to recall Flaminius before he should enter office in Gaul (Liv. 21.63.11-12; see 217, Consuls). The account is dubious (CAH 8.43; Seeck Hermes 8 [1874] 153-166), but the names may be authentic (see on Terentius, Münzer, RE nos. 30 and 43)." ;
	dprr:hasID 1313 .
